<FORM name="the_form" action="dEventCond.jsp" method="post" onSubmit="return check_form();">
	
   <p>To report an injury or illness go to the <a href="https://www.ehs.uci.edu/apps/hr/" >Report an Injury</a> page.</a></p>
					  <p>Use this form to report a safety concern, e.g.  a non-life threatening hazard, or  hazardous event or condition. This information can also be submitted by calling  EH&S at (949) 824-6200.</p>         
<hr>

      <p >When did the dangerous event or hazardous condition occur?</p>
      
      <p>Date/Time: &nbsp;<input id="i_date" name="i_date" type="text" value="" >&nbsp;<a href="javascript: NewCssCal('i_date','mmddyyyy','arrow',true,12,false)"><img src="images/cal.gif" style="width:16;height:16;"  alt="Pick a date"></a></p>
 <p>&nbsp;</p><fieldset>
      <p><legend>Did the incident occur in a lab or was the incident related to research activities?</legend></p>
      <p><INPUT type="radio" value="Yes" name="in_lab" >&nbsp;YES &nbsp;&nbsp;<INPUT type="radio" value="No" name="in_lab" >&nbsp;NO</p></fieldset>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>    
       <p>Provide the location of unsafe condition or hazard:<br>
       (e.g., Bldg/Rm or Parking Lot, Interior/Exterior, nearby landmark )</p>
      <p><textarea name="location" style="width:100%" ></textarea></p>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>
      <p>Describe the unsafe condition, event or hazard (e.g., chemical, biological, etc): </p>
      <p><textarea name="description" style="width:100%"></textarea></p>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>
 <p>If you would like to be contacted regarding this information, please provide your name and email address:&nbsp;(optional)</p>
 <p>Name: &nbsp;&nbsp;<INPUT type="text" value="" name="name" ></p>
 <p>Email: &nbsp;&nbsp;<INPUT type="text" value="" name="email" ></p>
      
      <p style="text-align:center;"> <input type="hidden" value="1" name="requestStage"></p>
        <p style="text-align:center;"> <input type="submit" name="Submit" value="Submit"></p>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>
      <p>It is illegal for any California employer to take action against employees who exercise their right under the law to report perceived
          or actual unsafe and/or unhealthy conditions or hazards to their employer. Reprisal to employees for exercising their right for safety and healthy
          related activities will not be tolerated.</p>
 
   
      

